Package: phototweetr
Title: A simple twitter bot that tweets photos
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jonathan",
           family = "Keane",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jkeane@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7087-9776"))
Description: Periodically tweets out photos that are found in a directory. It 
    extracts the EXIF metadata creating descriptions based on that.
